{"tid":92376,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"零售爆！去年訪港客中國客挫6.7%","createTime":"2017-01-23T14:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T02:45:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc032ecae398b831e914b77303643a3118981bc","tid":92376,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"香港旅遊發展局公布去年全年訪港旅客數字，整體訪港訪港旅客約5665.5萬人次，比2015年下跌4.5%。訪港中國旅客下跌6.7%，有4200多萬人次；國際旅客則上升3.1%，約有1300多萬。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局主席林建岳指，訪港中國旅客下跌主要因「一周一行」措施效應。而國際旅客整體數字上升3.1%，其中過夜旅客升幅更達5.7%。上年訪港的過夜旅客約有2655.3萬人次，以短途市場的升幅較顯著，達到8.4%，其中來自南韓、菲律賓及泰國的過夜旅客，增幅達雙位數字，同時亦突破過往紀錄。至於來自長途市場的過夜數字，則錄得2.8%按年增長。"},{"pid":"de43bc4977dd1420aa14d3a50b7bf32094715775","tid":92376,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:14:54.000Z","msg":"中國旅客 跌.......其實無乜用<br />\n<br />\n因為中國新移民, 中國「專才」「優才」 , 中國大學生, 中國國企員工..........每日都成千上萬衝來香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e4f81b67af6ee35a9ead50cfa6f8faaeed0e8d","tid":92376,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e816d3c615814bd968fb71f743bd559d1d5b04a5","tid":92376,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"一時話升，一時話跌，好撚亂"},{"pid":"58e04afd45f1c18216d38ff31d9da076be463f98","tid":92376,"uid":78118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:45:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc9240b9391f5c067ea504fc3b4141b435fdc1ca","tid":92376,"uid":7632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:38:06.000Z","msg":"我要跌67%<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17047fa32800aa8a94e848bcdcf46f929a5d744b","tid":92376,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:45:55.000Z","msg":"仲係好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class